147
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,230
Aku Zhuge Heng.

148
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:17,030
Demi bertemu Senior Ye,
aku khusus memilih

149
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:18,790
