mengangkut garam ke pantai?

178
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:57,110
Kita juga bisa mengadakan
tamasya menikmati fajar di laut.

179
00:09:57,710 --> 00:10:00,670
Ini juga usaha yang menguntungkan.

180
00:10:01,990 --> 00:10:02,510
Bagus.

181
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:03,590
Bagus!

182
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:05,030
Bagus sekali!

183
00:10:05,430 --> 00:10:07,470
